    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">These tough blocks are a fantastic tool to use for sharpening and smoothing all kinds of surfaces. Ideal for making a clean, sharp surface on tools, blades, molds, &amp; most metals that require sharpening or smoothing. The sharpening blocks are extremely hard and durable, making sharpening any surface a breeze! This set comes with 3 different blocks: fine, medium, and coarse grits. Each block is 6&quot; x 2&quot;, allowing a large surface for ease of use.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Diamond Sharpening Stone Knife and Blade Variety Coarse Grit Universal Set of 3</h2>\n  <p>These tough blocks are a fantastic tool to use for sharpening and smoothing all kinds of surfaces. Ideal for making a clean, sharp surface on tools, blades, molds, &amp; most metals that require sharpening or smoothing.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>3 Layers of Diamonds, Nickel-Bonded to a Heavy-Duty Alloy Steel Frame</li>\n    <li>User Friendly | Very Simple</li>\n    <li>Ergonomic Design for Ease of Use and Comfortable Grips</li>\n    <li><strong>Block Grit:</strong> 150 | 300 | 400</li>\n    <li><strong>Dimensions:</strong> 6&quot; x 2&quot; (LW)</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/